database server, and platform. Secure settings should be defined, implemented, and maintained, as defaults are often insecure. Additionally, software should be kept up to date.\",\n										          \"\",\n										          \"Evidence\"\n										        ],\n										        \"width\": [\n										          \"1\",\n										          \"6\",\n										          \"3\",\n										          \"2\"\n										        ],\n										        \"rows\": [\n										          [\n										            {\n										              \"type\": \"text\",\n										              \"value\": \"G.5.1\"\n										            },\n										            {\n										              \"type\": \"textandcomments\",\n													  \"id\": \"CFAAnnexGG5G51\",\n										              \"value\": \"<p><span class=\\\"panel-span-medium\\\">Are components of the software stack up to date? (i.e., Web Server, Application Server, DBMS, code libraries, etc.)</span></p>\"\n										            },\n										            {\n										              \"type\": \"radio\",\n										              \"paramname\": \"CFAAnnexGG5G51Radio\",\n										              \"options\": [\n										                \"Yes\",\n										                \"No\",\n										                \"N/A\"\n										              ]\n										            },\n										            {\n										              \"type\": \"textarea\",\n										              \"paramname\": \"CFAAnnexGG5G51Comments\",\n										              \"rows\": \"2\"\n										            }\n										          ],\n										          [\n										            {\n										              \"type\": \"text\",\n										              \"value\": \"G.5.2\"\n										            },\n										            {\n										              \"type\": \"textandcomments\",\n													  \"id\": \"CFAAnnexGG5G52\",\n										              \"value\": \"<p><span class=\\\"panel-span-medium\\\">Are unnecessary features disabled? (i.e., ports, services, pages, accounts, etc.)